"title": "8701: affluence",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8701",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Literally, “flowing” with prosperity. Wealth is not condemned in Scripture but is seen as a good gift of God. However, affluence has its dangers.</p>\n<h2>Godly affluence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:8\">EXO 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:1-Deut28:6\">DEU 28:1–28:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:11\">DEU 28:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:3\">PSA 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:3\">PSA 112:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:18-Prov8:21\">PRO 8:18–8:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:4\">PRO 22:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:5\">ISA 60:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:6\">ISA 61:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:12\">ISA 66:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:4\">MIC 4:4</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of affluence</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:8-Gen2:12\">GEN 2:8–2:12</a> <em>Eden</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:2\">GEN 13:2</a> <em>Abraham</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:12-Gen26:13\">GEN 26:12–26:13</a> <em>Isaac</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen33:11\">GEN 33:11</a> <em>Jacob</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:10-Job42:12\">JOB 42:10–42:12</a> <em>Job</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:13\">1KI 3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:23-1Kgs10:29\">1KI 10:23–10:29</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:27-2Chr32:29\">2CH 32:27–32:29</a> <em>Hezekiah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:57\">MAT 27:57</a> <em>Joseph of Arimathea</em></p>\n<h2>The dangers of affluence</h2>\n<h3>Pride</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:17-Deut8:18\">DEU 8:17–8:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:4-Ps10:6\">PSA 10:4–10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:3-Ps73:6\">PSA 73:3–73:6</a></p>\n<h3>Reliance upon riches</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:28\">PRO 11:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:10\">PSA 62:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:5\">PRO 23:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:19\">ECC 10:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:24\">MRK 10:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:16–12:21</a></p>\n<h3>Over-attachment to riches</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:22\">MAT 19:22</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:22\">MRK 10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:23\">LUK 18:23</a></p>\n<h3>Greed for more riches</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:10\">ECC 5:10</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Temptation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:9-1Tim6:10\">1TI 6:9–6:10</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Cares and anxieties</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:22\">MAT 13:22</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:19\">MRK 4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:14\">LUK 8:14</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual complacency</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:17\">REV 3:17</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Contempt for God</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:8-Prov30:9\">PRO 30:8–30:9</a></p>\n<h3>Contempt for the poor or unfortunate</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:5\">JOB 12:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:16\">PRO 22:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:6-Amos2:8\">AMO 2:6–2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:1\">AMO 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:11\">AMO 5:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:24-Luke16:31\">LUK 16:24–16:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:1-Jas5:6\">JAS 5:1–5:6</a></p>\n<h2>Affluence is temporary</h2>\n<h3>It is for this life only</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:7\">1TI 6:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:21\">JOB 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:35-Ps37:36\">PSA 37:35–37:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:10-Ps49:12\">PSA 49:10–49:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:16-Ps49:20\">PSA 49:16–49:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:15\">ECC 5:15</a></p>\n<h3>It is often lost</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:13-Job1:15\">JOB 1:13–1:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:13-Eccl5:14\">ECC 5:13–5:14</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual affluence</h2>\n<h3>The riches of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:19\">PHP 4:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:7-Ps36:9\">PSA 36:7–36:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:9\">2CO 9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:8\">EPH 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual wealth</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:3\">EPH 1:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:4\">1PE 1:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:9\">REV 2:9</a></p>\n<h3>The shared wealth of the church</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:29-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:29–10:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:34-Acts4:35\">ACT 4:34–4:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:18\">PHP 4:18</a></p>\n<h3>The wealth of heaven</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:20\">MAT 6:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:33\">LUK 12:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:16-Rev7:17\">REV 7:16–7:17</a></p>",
